This project covers 'Optical Character Recognition' along with applications of 'Bayes Theorem' and 'ROC Curve' in 'Statistical Pattern Recognition' course. 
Specifically, applications of 'Bayesian Decision Theory' in 'Classification' and 'Segmentation' tasks.
This folder contains 'Questions File', 'Report File', and 'Implementations' in python programming language.
Also, the processed data in the project may be added.
